T|21 ·|0|The intake for the software factory — proposed pd/bd ideas that can become projects in the Software Pipeline. Sidebar badge: 94.
T|21 ·|1|
T|Purp|0|A continuously growing feed of ideas for things to bd (pd, features, tools). It's the top of the Software Factory funnel: ideas accumulate here (badge shows 94), the best get promoted into the Software Pipeline as projects/PRs.
T|Purp|1|
X|What|0|A stream of idea cards — pd concepts, feature ideas, internal tools — likely sourced from the owner, ag, Isaac's tn, and Advisory Council recommendations.
X|What|1|Triage actions per card: promote to a project (into Software Pipeline), defer, or reject — consistent w/ the ap/defer/reject pattern used across the app.
X|What|2|Tagging by workspace and tp; the large badge (94) implies a backlog that gets filtered down.
X|What|3|
T|Rela|0|Feeds Software Pipeline (22) where promoted ideas become coded projects (Nexus) under QA (Steve).
T|Rela|1|Receives inputs from tn Radar (20) and Advisory Council (03).
